						<span class="section-label">Checkpoint</span>
						<h2 id="base-model-title" class="promise">The psychology of a base model.</h2>
						<p class="body-copy body-copy--short">
							At this point, we have a trained internet-text generator. Powerful, but not yet a helpful assistant.
						</p>
