					<ul class="checkpoint-list">
						<li>Token-level internet document simulator.</li>
						<li>Stochastic and probabilistic. Run it again and you may sample a different continuation.</li>
						<li>It dreams internet documents one token at a time.</li>
						<li>A lot of useful world knowledge is stored in the network parameters.</li>
						<li>You can already build applications with clever prompts: few-shot translation, in-context learning, or a conversation-shaped assistant prompt.</li>
						<li>But we can make it better.</li>
					</ul>
